-- Credit Agricole Said to Hire Banks for Euro Covered Bond Sale
-- B y   P a u l   A r m s t r o n g
-- 2011-12-30T12:30:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-30/credit-agricole-said-to-hire-banks-for-euro-covered-bond-sale.html
Credit Agricole SA (ACA)  hired banks to
lead a covered bond issue in euros early in the New Year,
according to a banker involved in the transaction.  Danske Bank A/S (DANSKE) , Societe Generale SA, UBS AG and  UniCredit
SpA (UCG)  will help Credit Agricole manage the sale, which is expected
to be triple-A rated by all three major ratings firms, the
banker said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Armstrong at 
 parmstrong10@bloomberg.net  